description:
When it comes to gift giving, it's the thought that counts and nothing is more thoughtful than a homemade food gift! Bonus points if it tastes delicious! Here are 4 simple, inexpensive, and delicious homemade gifts that will surely delight your loved ones. Not to mention, the gift wrap uses materials that you probably already have in your house. So skip the holiday rush at the mall and turn on some holiday music in the kitchen and get to cooking. Happy Holidays!

RECIPES mentioned in the video (All Vegan):
******** Persimmon Cookies: http://myeclectickitchen.com/tag/vegan-and-gluten-free-persimmon-cookies

******** Chocolate Truffles: http://www.astigvegan.com/veganchocolatetruffles/

********  Buko Pie:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=99qP1JjKLuU

********  Bibingka Cakes:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fzAlwQcxieI
